The Sorcerer Supreme has been SHOT! When the Sanctum Sanctorum is broken into and Dr. Strange is shot, it's up to the veteran magic-user to track down the culprits and retrieve one of the most sought-after items he has even been in possession of...a cure for all disease. Can the former surgeon solve the mystery and save the world from a mysterious and malicious threat? Tune in to our review of Dr. Strange: The Oath and find out! If you're a Dr. Strange fan, this episode is can't miss and just what the doctor ordered. Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

